                "post_type": "page",
                "title": "Neighborhood Cookout Plan",
                "content": "<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Summer Cookout Plan</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Join neighbors for a relaxed summer cookout with grilled favorites, simple sides, cold drinks, and time to catch up outdoors.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul>\n<li>Confirm the cookout date, time, and shared outdoor space.</li>\n<li>Coordinate grills, seating, plates, napkins, and serving tables.</li>\n<li>Ask neighbors to sign up for sides, desserts, drinks, or cleanup help.</li>\n</ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:buttons -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons\"><!-- wp:button -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-button\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link wp-element-button\" href=\"#menu\">View menu</a></div>\n<!-- /wp:button --></div>\n<!-- /wp:buttons -->",
